DCT

site = "https://pegasus1.pegasusgateway.com/api"
auth <- list (
  username = "developer@digitalcomtech.com"
  )
raw_query <- list(   
  vids = "617,197,700,863,909,639",
  #vids = "617,197,700", #good for mph density
  from = "2015-5-1",
  to = "2015-10-15",
  fields = "base,rssi:@cf_rssi,vi:'vid:'+@vid__str,mph,valid_position,comdelay,type,vid,label,code,lat,lon,hdop",
  filter = "(valid_position and mph > 5 and comdelay < 3600 and hdop < 3 and rssi < 32)",
  export = "tsv",
  async = "1",
  types="10"
  )

data <- getPegasusRawData(site, auth, raw_query, iters=40, token=NULL, poll_secs=3)
